---
title: Smoked Salmon Rigatoni with baby spinach and cream cheese
description: The fat in this salmon is counteracted beautifully with the addition of bright lemon and piquant chilli. Al dente rigatoni may just make for the perfect combination in this seafood pasta dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R15_W46_IE_IECF29785-6_Main_high-f81a1d2c.jpg
